Try the plugin at: http://sd.linksalpha.com

Enables Social Sharing of your blog posts to 30+ Social Networks, including:

  1. Google +1
  2. Facebook Like
  3. Facebook Send
  4. Twitter button
  5. LinkedIn Share
  6. Pinterest
  7. StumbleUpon
  8. Digg
  9. Reddit
  10. Email

  1. Facebook Profile/Wall
  2. Facebook Pages
  3. Facebook Groups
  4. Facebook Events
  5. Facebook Share
  6. Twitter
  7. LinkedIn
  8. MySpace
  9. Yammer
  10. Yahoo
  11. Identi.ca
  12. Status.net
  13. Socialcast
  14. Plurk
  15. Sonico
  16. Delicious
